content: I've been getting around 7-8 hours of sleep each night, but I've noticed that I tend to feel more energized on Mondays and Tuesdays, and then my energy levels dip on Wednesdays, probably due to the meetings I mentioned earlier. I've been feeling a bit worn out after last week, so I think I'll focus on getting some extra rest this week and then try to adjust my wake-up time gradually.
